FBIS3-17386 "drsov058_f_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-058 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Mar 1994 National Affairs Meshkov Orders Crimea Switch to Moscow Time 27 Mar LD2403193094 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1855 GMT 24 Mar 94 LD2403193094 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [Report by UKRINFORM correspondent Lev Ryabchikov for TASS] [Text] Simferopol 24 March, TASS -- Crimean President Yuriy Meshkov signed a decree on Thursday ordering the Republic to switch to Moscow time beginning 27 March. The decision will also affect all railway, water, air and inter-city automobile transportation and communication services. Enterprises and organisation will switch to the new regime on Monday, 28 March.
